Found out there is a 'truncate' filter also available (8.6+), so I'm using it like this:
<ComponentName>{{!!propalias ? ': ' + (propalias | ncRichText | truncate:true:150) : ''}}


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

{{propalias | ncRichText | truncate:true:100}}
